    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Map of northern portion of Brazil showing the distribution of Schizodon paucisquamis (yellow dot; yellow star: type locality), S. trivittatus (orange dots), S. vittatus (blue dots) and S. fasciatus (red dots). Rivers indicated as follows: 1. Amazonas, 2. Tapajós, 3. Xingu, 4. Araguaia, 5. Tocantins. Some symbols may represent more than one sampling locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8249238/files/figure.png" ;
